TextEng: I would speak with you... and perhaps more.
Text: 당신과 이야기하고 싶어요... 어쩌면 그 이상도요.

TextEng: Me talk with yous? Maybe more?
Goodbye.
<StartAction>Bemoan about how no one really respects you.</Start>
Let's talk about you, and what you like.
You listen well? Does talking make your "clients" more relaxed?
Text: 말 잘 들어줘? 손님들이랑 이야기하면 더 편해져?

TextEng: Perhaps I could ask some serious questions?
We talk about you. You pretty.
You listen? Talking make customers feel more happy?
Text: 너 들어줘? 말하면 손님들 기분 더 좋아져?

TextEng: Maybe me ask serious stuffs, okay?
Where are you from? What is your story?
Where you from? What your story?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> I'd find it degrading to disguise my true self like that.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 진짜 자신을 숨기는 건, 제겐 모욕처럼 느껴져요.

TextEng: I want to talk about something else.
Me talk about different things.
<StartAction>Lament the inherent loneliness of the adventurer lifestyle.</Start>
Nothing bothers me. I am strong.
Me strong. Nothing hurt me.
Text: 나 튼튼해. 아무것도 못 아프게 해.

TextEng: Whatever, harlot. I'm not here to talk.
Text: 됐어, 창녀. 수다 떨러 온 게 아니야.

TextEng: Shaddap. Me not here for words, lap-lady.
Text: 닥쳐. 난 말하러 온 거 아냐, 접대 아가씨.

TextEng: There's more than talking, right?
We not just talk, right?
Here is a Pass Coin. My name is <FirstName>.
Here my Pass Coin. Me called <FirstName>.
I don't have a Pass Coin.
Me not gots Pass Coin.
I should be going.
Me should go, maybe.
I'll stay a while, I think.
Me not so dumb. Me stay.
I must leave. Farewell.
Me gots to go. Bye.
Perhaps we could... retire to your bedchambers, my lady?
Text: 혹시... 당신의 침실로 함께 갈까요, 아가씨?

TextEng: Maybe we go sleep now? Nicely, I mean.
Let's knock boots, honey!
Let's make two-butt beast!
What do you know of the plague?
Know anything about plague?
Shouldn't you be ashamed of working here?
You feel dirty? Maybe ashamed?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> That's very selfless, giving of yourself like that.
Harsh. Aren't you supposed to have a heart of gold?
Harsh. Where's your heart of gold and stuff?
Text: 차갑네. 황금 같은 마음은 어디 갔어?

TextEng: <StartAction>Confide that you might have a big role in curing the plague.</Start>
Text: <StartAction>역병 치료에 큰 역할을 맡을지도 모른다고 속내를 털어놓습니다.</Start>

TextEng: What's that about your other clients?
You gots problems with someone?
You're having problems? Perhaps it *should* be my business.
Text: 곤란한 일이 있나요? 제 일이 되어도 상관없겠네요.

TextEng: You gots trouble? Maybe it good me help, maybe?
Don't tease! Tell me about your client or shut the hell up!
Text: 애태우지 마! 손님 얘기를 하든가 입을 다물어!

TextEng: Stupid! Say about client or be more quiets!
Text: 바보야! 손님 얘기해, 아니면 조용히 해!

TextEng: What's in it for me?
What me get?
Perhaps I can look into it. I'll see.
Text: 제가 알아볼 수도 있겠네요. 고려해 보죠.

TextEng: Maybe me try find this jerk.
I'll maybe take a look. Now, about that chat?
Me maybe look, but first we talk.
Text: 나 볼지도 몰라. 근데 먼저 얘기하자.

TextEng: I'll just go look into this.
Me go check it out.
I'm here as a Moonstone Mask customer.
Me here for pretty ladies. Heeh.
Text: 나 예쁜 아가씨 보러 왔지. 히히.

TextEng: What business do you mean? Are you having trouble?
Text: 무슨 일 말씀이죠? 곤란한 일이라도 있나요?

TextEng: I'm here about the business with Hoff.
Me here about Hoff.
What business you mean? Me don't get it.
I hope you enjoyed our time together.
Hope you happy. Me happy if you happy.
Like I care? You're another notch on my sword.
Text: 내 알 바야? 넌 그저 목록에 하나 더 늘었을 뿐.

TextEng: Heh... me not care. Got what me wanted.
Text: 헤... 상관없어. 내가 원한 건 얻었거든.

TextEng: Goodbye.
Here's your brooch. Hoff doesn't have it.
Text: 여기 당신 브로치. 호프가 가진 건 없었어요.

TextEng: Here brooch. Hoff gots nothing.
Hoff is dead. Here is your brooch.
Hoff whack dead! Here your brooch.
Text: 호프 꽝! 죽었어! 여기 네 브로치.

TextEng: Sorry to hear that.
That too bad.
He's dead. Here's your brooch.
Text: 그 자는 죽었어요. 브로치는 여기 있습니다.

TextEng: He dead. Here your pin-thing.
Nothing.
He's scared now. Here's your brooch.
Text: 이제 겁을 먹었더군요. 브로치는 여기 있습니다.

TextEng: He scaredy-baby now. Here your brooch.
Well good. Now, how about some chatting?
Text: 잘 됐네요. 그럼, 대화를 좀 더 해볼까요?

TextEng: Good then. Now maybe we "talk."
Hoff? Was he a half-Orc? He's already dead.
This Hoff guy, he half-orc? He dead.
